{"tid":613183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集結連登力量 四月一日夜晚八點向名校secret開戰（4）","createTime":"2018-04-01T12:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T13:11:16.000Z","uid":153600,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4c62c2b6721c6386672fcdada58fea545b5484","tid":613183,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">作戰計劃</span></div></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四月一日 晚上八點 正式開戰！</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">由於之前我哋準備不足，所以開戰日期改為今晚八點，不便之處，敬請原諒 </div> </strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【未清楚事情始未嘅可以去 <span style=\"color: gold;\">#2</span> 睇返懶人包】</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">----------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">速攻 (大約持續一小時)</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. Instagram 留言</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鑑於而家嘅中學生都係用IG多，所以我哋主打嘅戰場會係IG。<br />\nIG account: schools.secrets<br />\n<br />\n我哋會喺最近嘅幾個post以留言形式黎表達我哋嘅訴求，歡迎大家自行發揮，或者可以用以下嘅懶人包發動攻擊：<br />\n<br />\n名校secrets管理員極醜惡　曲解投稿內容　事後刪帖欲息事<br />\n事件詳情:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n請大家unfollow此page<br />\n強烈要求名校secrets公開澄清及道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺IG開新account係非常容易，大家可以開定幾個古人account，或者用真身攻擊亦都無任歡迎。開新account流程如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/180513_672972adae9aa234bfba9e30e1d18c11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F180513_672972adae9aa234bfba9e30e1d18c11.jpg&h=70de8990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. Facebook 留言</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/schools.secrets/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fschools.secrets%2F&d=tgv2bwgRnohFOpTdGxuNZZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=73fc80ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/schools.secrets/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook comment可以加上圖片，所以我哋精心製作咗以下嘅大字報，歡迎大家使用：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/030432_22e1ff688cd401da77d350ae06c7a953.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F030432_22e1ff688cd401da77d350ae06c7a953.jpeg&h=2d1ada11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家亦可以加上上一段提過嘅文字懶人包，以加強攻勢。同樣大家亦可以開定古人account，準備全面進場！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 檢舉 Facebook Page </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(中文版)<br />\n舉報--&gt; 我認為這不應該出現在 Facebook --&gt; 這是仇恨言論 --&gt; 種族或民族 --&gt; 送交Facebook 審查<br />\n<br />\n(英文版)<br />\nReport --&gt; I think it shouldn't be on Facebook --&gt; It's hate speech --&gt; A race or ethnicity --&gt; Submit to Facebook for review<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 檢舉 Instagram Page </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(中文版)<br />\n檢舉 --&gt; 內容不適當 --&gt; I believe this account violates Instagram's community guidelines --&gt; Report account --&gt; Posting inappropriate content --&gt; Hate speech or symbols<br />\n<br />\n(英文版)<br />\nReport --&gt; It's inappropriate --&gt; I believe this account violates Instagram's community guidelines --&gt; Report account --&gt; Posting inappropriate content --&gt; Hate speech or symbols<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">----------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長期作戰計劃<br />\n(大約持續24小時)</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 瘋狂投稿 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n投稿link: <a href=\"https://schoolssecrets.formstack.com/forms/schools_secrets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fschoolssecrets.formstack.com%2Fforms%2Fschools_secrets&d=tgv2bwgRnohFOpTdGxuNZZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=07af1643\" target=\"_blank\">https://schoolssecrets.formstack.com/forms/schools_secrets</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋目標係要透過瘋狂投稿去令佢哋於至少一日內無法運作。為咗要令佢哋無辦法輕鬆篩選出廢文，我哋建議大家可以扮認真投稿，例如去佢哋facebook搵啲以往嘅文章，但係del走中間嘅部分，或者喺某小部分鳩打，令佢哋辛辛苦苦睇到大半先發現其實已經被玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n1. 唔好打粗口，咁樣佢哋例如可以filter by 「屌」，一見到有個「屌」字就成篇文唔使睇。<br />\n2. 唔好打「連登」兩個字，原因同上。<br />\n3. 唔好post重覆內容，佢哋可以remove duplicate posts。假如你有一篇千字文，每次改一隻字，然後再submit就ok。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. PM Facebook / Instagram Page </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由於佢哋接受private message作為投稿方法，我哋要透過PM轟炸佢哋去令佢哋於至少一日內無法運作。注意事項同上。"},{"pid":"abbc6727b67cde4da5323fabbaa5eeb578ecc794","tid":613183,"uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">名校secrets管理員</span><span style=\"color: red;\">極醜惡</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">行為</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曲解投稿內容</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">事後</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">刪帖</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">欲息事</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/184008_6bf675f7f9fc7513531bebb570793826.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F184008_6bf675f7f9fc7513531bebb570793826.png&h=a169ac35&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>事源：<br />\n會員#144982日前向名校secrets IG DM投稿</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182515_273ab85f1212b1f42c8b3db95e97a4da.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182515_273ab85f1212b1f42c8b3db95e97a4da.jpeg&h=5c4c84ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>事後於lihkg post:  <span style=\"font-size: small;\">名校secret係咪做緊資訊過濾? <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/610057/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/610057/page/1?ref=web</a></span>發現名校secrets管理員擅自於投稿附圖加上說明<br />\n會員#144982即時向名校secrets提出質詢為何未經許可便加上說明並要求出帖澄清投稿人並無此意</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182545_a28166ed799d577c124632ea5335feb0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182545_a28166ed799d577c124632ea5335feb0.jpeg&h=9518e592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182654_0483b9ff7d8c05f9f81f7bbc079834cc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182654_0483b9ff7d8c05f9f81f7bbc079834cc.jpeg&h=5f3512e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>但竟遭管理員無理拒絕 表示不會澄清 更未經投稿人同意刪除該帖</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182741_8083c439858da6d9d862c3aca7a4bf06.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182741_8083c439858da6d9d862c3aca7a4bf06.jpeg&h=637003a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>會員#144982再度追問 管理員再三推搪並狡辯稱出帖時經常為投稿內容加上說明<br />\n隨後則對追問已讀不回 打算不了了之</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182806_4b230f1cea14071def076ded09a239ae.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182806_4b230f1cea14071def076ded09a239ae.jpeg&h=af0c2035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一眾會員對名校secrets管理員之醜惡無恥行為怒不可遏<br />\n現嚴正要求名校secrets管理員：<br />\n1. </span><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>闡明</strong></span><span style=\"color: gold;\">為投稿加上說明之</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">準則</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 為曲解會員#144982投稿一事作</span><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>澄清</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 為曲解會員#144982投稿一事作</span><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">公開道歉</span></strong></span>["},{"pid":"226016d1957e0ba69295bd342753d3fe27c4016f","tid":613183,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d961a0dbd0e151085437bbd33d73340ceed3c6ee","tid":613183,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> 額外資料及精選留言<br />\n</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n由會員 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔知撬邊個好</span></strong> 提供<br />\n原post留言：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/12?ref=web&amp;post=298\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/12?ref=web&amp;post=298</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1.</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.richyli.com/tool/loremipsum/wordcount.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.richyli.com%2Ftool%2Floremipsum%2Fwordcount.asp&d=tgv2bwgRnohFOpTdGxuNZZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ee7d3c38\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.richyli.com/tool/loremipsum/wordcount.asp</a><br />\n繼續幫手推呢個網，幾千人一日放10篇去<a href=\"https://schoolmat.es/secrets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fschoolmat.es%2Fsecrets&d=tgv2bwgRnohFOpTdGxuNZZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=751fd97c\" target=\"_blank\">https://schoolmat.es/secrets</a>，然後兩三日出一篇堅但伏ge文，內容可以話政府，劏房波等等，扮係學生寫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2.</strong></span></span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">機佬</span></strong> 留言<br />\n原post留言：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/21?ref=web&amp;post=503\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/21?ref=web&amp;post=503</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">垃圾濫權page到底幾時可以摺埋？</span></strong><br />\n佢完全係社會縮影<br />\n由分享秘密 賺夠人氣 漸漸轉型到比中學生公開討論嘅一個page<br />\n性質都可以算叫做半討論區<br />\n但係班所謂admin<br />\n一嚟會過濾咗一啲對自己page不利（例如唔可以批評admin嘅處事手法）嘅訊息<br />\n二嚟會喺ig幫人哋啲相加caption 甚至曲解原post意思 加入自己個人睇法<br />\n三嚟會block同自己意見唔同嘅人 如喺GHS事件只要表露自己有少少支持連登都即block<br />\n四嚟admin啲態度 真係令我好懷疑佢哋係咪真係名校生 禮貌啲回覆查詢？ 佢會叫你 「死開啦」 「不嬲都係咁」<br />\n上面想講嘅嘢係<br />\n而加好明顯有一班人<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>恃住自己喺網絡上有些少權力<br />\n就任意操控訊息嘅流通<br />\n任意篩選一啲意見 以致成個page都好似一言堂咁</strong></span><br />\n最重要嘅係 有一大班中學生日日留意你哋page<br />\n而佢哋大部分都肯定唔知佢哋會篩選意見同留言<br />\n甚至喺post到加入自己個人意見<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>咁做同政府扼殺言論自由 有分別咩？</strong></span><br />\n我明白 佢哋可能認為自己唔係討論區<br />\n可以有權篩選意見或留言<br />\n但你絕可以喺page到開宗明義話自己會挑選一啲佢哋認為適合嘅post先post出嚟<br />\n咁樣會好好多<br />\n但而加就係好多人認為你會post哂所有意見<br />\n普羅大眾會將呢啲大致歸納為00後嘅意見<br />\n如近期繁簡之爭 可見 未被admin篩走嘅人好多都覺得簡體無問題<br />\n佢變相操控咗一大班學生嘅意見同民意<br />\n絕對係好危險嘅事情<br />\n仲有 佢哋為人處事 亦都好可能會影響一大班00後嘅思想<br />\n希望佢哋唔好再為害人間<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">巴絲打，聽日一齊推冧佢哋！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3.</strong></span></span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">可惜我是天秤座_</span></strong> 留言<br />\n原post留言：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/29?ref=web&amp;post=703\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/29?ref=web&amp;post=703</a><br />\n<br />\n推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以仼由支那文化繼續蹂躪香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>好明顯香港學校同網絡已經慢慢失守緊</strong></span><br />\n如果連呢啲都守唔住嘅話基本上香港前途就更加黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我地作為<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港人絕對有責任反擊</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而網絡就係第一步<br />\n但希望大家可以一齊打呢場低成本嘅網絡戰<br />\n反攻網絡反攻校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一步一步清剿支那文化<br />\n守往每一代香港人<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送多幅圖比大家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/001452_dcc47d110048f99e69e44eb852a76162.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F001452_dcc47d110048f99e69e44eb852a76162.png&h=997f0a1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cae5caa51a0fa94ebe152570694f9863c09efe1","tid":613183,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得投稿同舉報先係戲肉<br />\nCm只係前菜</span>"},{"pid":"3b8b7f0920a35d332d7c77d101b6d2c943ab4218","tid":613183,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/204915_1bb412410811e2adfbf8900b9ad77969.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F204915_1bb412410811e2adfbf8900b9ad77969.gif&h=539a9078&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"061c1b591445a8cc59c76267e011471d65e90480","tid":613183,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"咁快開定4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9975324d1f12a1cd63449e1332c1152aa61a71c4","tid":613183,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"061c1b591445a8cc59c76267e011471d65e90480","tid":613183,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"咁快開定4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"3好快就會爆<br />\n開定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26933867fa4f25ed39c78423dd83bb9bee539d8","tid":613183,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cae5caa51a0fa94ebe152570694f9863c09efe1","tid":613183,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得投稿同舉報先係戲肉<br />\nCm只係前菜</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"已投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只怕佢唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d131755beefbe30f89361be8b559238fa8b7d8e6","tid":613183,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse